name: __ETileMapProjectionMode
doc: The different kinds of projection modes supported

IsometricDiamond: Isometric tile layout (shaped like a diamond) */
IsometricStaggered: Isometric tile layout (roughly in a square with alternating rows staggered).  Warning: Not fully supported yet.
HexagonalStaggered: Hexagonal tile layout (roughly in a square with alternating rows staggered).  Warning: Not fully supported yet.
